{"tid":807129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"代購店聲稱獲政府百萬資助！網民怒：公然資助黃牛黨？","createTime":"2018-09-05T09:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T10:18:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"73b4cf9c268d91ff2cac7de7ea51b33905b99a9c","tid":807129,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2150000/2154148/gg02--_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2150000%2F2154148%2Fgg02--_1024.jpg&h=95542b20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然現在全球的物流行業發達，大家想購買其他國家的產品已經比以前容易得多，然而並不是人人都有渠道，所以代購行業就應運而生。正常來説，大家都習慣了代購價格會比起商品價格高，畢竟代購商都要賺錢，價格不太過份的話就皆大歡喜。然而當一間代購公司聲稱成功獲得政府批出過百萬港元的資助，就引起爭議了。<br />\n<br />\n有日本代購店以「政府支（資）助大家買玩具」為題，表示成功獲得政府「青年發展基金」批出接近七位數的資助金額。而店鋪會由即日開始實踐計劃書内容，如「引入唔同版本產品」同「大幅調低價格」。然而，這家網店主要提供「個人化代購服務」，以高價幫客人代購日本商品。由玩具、手辦，到 CD、會場商品、畫冊，以至是動漫相關的手機、耳機，演唱會門票等都有涉獵。如數年前大熱的「&mu;'s Final LoveLive」演唱會，當選門票價格就曾以 $5000 一張發售，十分誇張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2150000/2154148/gg1_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2150000%2F2154148%2Fgg1_600.png&h=d2429851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，有網民就感到十分不滿。他們認爲代購根本就是「無本生利」、「另類黃牛」，爲何能夠成功通過政府審批？有網民留言說：「拎政府錢做代購係爽嘅」、「20 算變 10 算？」、「之前炒 lovelive 飛啲水應該都夠佢住山頂啦」、「政府公然資助黃牛黨垃_圾」、「政府批俾佢天無眼」、「幫襯佢果啲比佢咁食水法都未清醒」、「政府同奸商互惠互利係定律」、「接近 3 倍價錢買佢真係仲賺過出產嘅商人」、「批一球俾佢做生意，犀利」、「賣 fig 住山頂不是夢」。雖然網民都對代購店成功申請政府資助表示不解，但由於代購店未有公開資助的詳細內容，現階段也難以確定資助金額的用途。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2150000/2154148/gg4_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2150000%2F2154148%2Fgg4_600.jpg&h=377ce75f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2154148/代購店聲稱獲政府百萬資助！網民怒：公然資助黃牛黨？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2154148%2F%E4%BB%A3%E8%B3%BC%E5%BA%97%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E7%8D%B2%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%EF%BC%81%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%80%92%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%AC%E7%84%B6%E8%B3%87%E5%8A%A9%E9%BB%83%E7%89%9B%E9%BB%A8%EF%BC%9F&d=UacojdqbEYzd%2Fs7TQUlVLJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=d3d42062\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2154148/代購店聲稱獲政府百萬資助！網民怒：公然資助黃牛黨？</a>"},{"pid":"4352d65f30b60694a252c0f020c490a361d620df","tid":807129,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"政府真係多錢到冇地方洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5439ddeff91abe0a51ca84174092e4cb36399958","tid":807129,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"𠵱間野，我上網買比埋錢轉運都平過係佢到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281fa08bdd7532d8d23310fee0052f191559438e","tid":807129,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:45:38.000Z","msg":"代購做做下就變代理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168db592cecb4ce591637041c184cc5f869a8673","tid":807129,"uid":164799,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"政府批錢個班成日當唔係自己錢亂尻黎<br />\n公務員又好少炒最多比冇得升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886e528d9f4a88bd5209cd7824d60ed14b911a3b","tid":807129,"uid":4493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"比人起到間嘢紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843a9